text.section:
In this section, "claim information" means information regarding:
whether an individual is receiving, has received, or has applied for benefits under this title;
the amount of benefits an individual is receiving or is entitled to receive;
an individual's current or most recent home address;
whether an individual has refused an offer of work and if so, a description of the job offered, including terms, conditions, and rate of pay; and
any other information that is needed by the child support enforcement unit to verify eligibility for and the amount of benefits.
